# The release workflow checks the paylod monorepo out here to supply the canonical Daraja catalog.
# actions/checkout refuses a path outside the workspace, so it cannot be a sibling there as it is
# locally. Ignored so that the post-sweep `git status --porcelain` clean-tree assertion sees only
# what the harness touched.
.mpesa-canonical/
